openaiSpec.name: search_books

q.description: The query string for searching books.

place.description: The place that the book to search for mentions in its content.

title.description: The title of the book to search for.

author.description: The author of the book to search for.

offset.description: The starting point of the results to be returned. Default is 0.

person.description: The person or character whom the book to search for mentions in its content.

subject.description: The subject of the book to search for.

language.description: The language code to filter results (e.g., 'spa' for Spanish). Use ISO 639-3 language codes.

openaiSpec.description: Search for books in the Open Library database by title, author, subject, place, person, language, or general query.

userSettings.name: sort
userSettings.label: Sort Order
userSettings.description: Choose how to sort the results.

userSettings.name: publish_year_from
userSettings.label: Publish Year From
userSettings.description: Enter the starting year for the publish year range.

userSettings.name: publish_year_to
userSettings.label: Publish Year To
userSettings.description: Enter the ending year for the publish year range.

userSettings.name: limit
userSettings.label: Limit
userSettings.description: Enter the maximum number of results to return (number only).
